Cyberpunk style: A towering obsidian vault door embedded in a neon-lit server room, its surface covered in intricate glowing circuit patterns and multiple biometric locks. Six holographic handprint scanners pulse in different colors around the door's perimeter. In the foreground, scattered across a dark metallic floor, lie cracked and discarded USB drives and old floppy disks emanating faint corrupted data streams. The atmosphere is thick with tension—cyan and magenta light cuts through digital fog while encrypted data particles float in the air like fireflies. The vault appears impenetrable, ancient yet futuristic, guarding something of immense digital value. Reflective surfaces show fragmented glimpses of shadowy figures. The entire scene conveys the weight of protecting a critical secret in a world where everything can be copied, stolen, or compromised.
